import { Box, Container } from '@mui/system';
import React from 'react';
import { useTheme } from '@emotion/react';
import { 
    FormControlLabel,
    Checkbox,
    Typography,
    } from '@mui/material';
import DeleteForeverIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DeleteForever';

const ItemList=()=>{
    const theme = useTheme();
    const colorgrey1 = theme.palette.gray1.main;
    const colorgrey2 = theme.palette.gray2.main;
    const colorgrey3 = theme.palette.gray3.main;
    return(
        <Box
        display='flex'
        flexDirection='row'
        height='157px'
        borderBottom='1px solid #BDBDBD'
        mb='10px'
        >
            <Checkbox sx={{
                mb:'20px',
                mr:'35px',
            }}/>
            <Box
            component='img'
            src = "./Ramen.png"
            width = '200px'
            height = '133px'
            />
            <Container
            display="flex"
            flexDirection="column"
            alignItems="flex-start"
            gap='8px'>
                <Typography fontWeight={400} fontSize='16px' sx={{color: colorgrey3}}>
                    Asian
                </Typography>
                <Typography fontWeight={600} fontSize='24px' sx={{color: colorgrey1}}>
                    Ichiraku Ramen
                </Typography>
                <Typography fontWeight={400} fontSize='18px' sx={{color: colorgrey2}}>
                    Ichiraku Ramen
                </Typography>
                <Typography fontWeight={600} fontSize='20px' color='secondary'>
                    IDR 300.000
                </Typography>

            </Container>
            <DeleteForeverIcon
            fontSize="large"
            sx={{
                color: '#EB5757',
                mt:"40px"
            }}/>

        </Box>
    );
};



const Checkout = () => {
  return (
    <Box 
    display="flex"
    flexDirection="column"
    >
    <Container>
        <Box
        display='flex'
        flexDirection='column'
        alignItems='flex-start'
        height='50px'
        borderBottom='1px solid #BDBDBD'
        mt='40px'
        mb='24px'
        >
            <FormControlLabel
            value="selectAll"
            control={<Checkbox />}
            label="Pilih Semua"
            labelPlacement="end"
            sx={{
                gap:'35px',
                
            }}/>
        </Box>
            <ItemList/>
            <ItemList/>
            <ItemList/>

    </Container>
    <Box
    position="fixed"
    width="100%"
    height="100px"
    display="flex"
    alignItems="flex-end"
    bottom='0px'
    borderTop="1px solid #BDBDBD"
    sx={{
        filter: 'drop-shadow(0px -2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25))'
    }}
    >
    </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Checkout
